Tutorials¶

Installation¶

git clone https://github.com/cookieMonster21/verify_uuid.git
cd verify_uuid/src
pip3 install -r requirements.txt

Starting¶

  • Open help menu with all available functions:

python3 main.py -h

  • Further usage options with detailed instructions on specific questions can be found in the How-To Guides.
